{
  "stem": "8725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were nuns in that hospital in Radom, but there were students, not-- they were students like me, girls.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were also older nurses, finished nurses, that were also not nuns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first, I was just interested to learn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to be the best.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So with the girls, I didn't go to movies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted my parents to be proud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not-- at that moment, I did not think that I will be a-- I wanted to study first.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And before we really started, Hitler was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were there any non-Jewish women in this nursing school?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, to me, this would not have made it any difference.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I didn't make it any particular-- I don't-- I don't know if there were, I cannot tell you that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, because many of the girls were going with boys and interested-- and I-- my interest was not such.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was 17, going on 18, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my interest was not really with-- with boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was, as a youngster, I did have the beginning of tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was developing rather late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was not interested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I thought I am ugly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought myself-- my sister, Janina, that was one year younger, she was developing little breasts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I did not like myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I will not tell you that-- I did not have any boys looking at me or I looking for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were with my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, and just before [INAUDIBLE] we start to hearing that the-- 1938-- that the Germans were-- wanted to go fight with Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was 200 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like everything, we did not believe it, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
